{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-02-09-S",
 "title": "Battle of Wistril",
 "summary": "A New Republic task force led by the Mon Calamari cruiser NRSC Deliverance jumps into the eerily quiet Wistril system, escorting Archer A-wings, Ghost and Rogue X-wings, and Draco bomber squadrons to seize Imperial supply canisters in orbit. They are met by the Victory-class Star Destroyer Volatile and four squadrons of TIE fighters that scramble from the planet and the destroyer. In the swirling dogfight the Ghost pilots take losses through reckless flying, Commodore Snunb directs warhead fire at a weakened starboard shield generator, and the fighters pour torpedoes into the Volatile's shields and engines. The Deliverance and its gunship hammer the destroyer until its engines die and the ship breaks apart in a final explosion, after which the surviving New Republic fighters disperse and move on toward the planet and its captured cargo.",
